ege]]\n|-\n| 1989\n| [[Blackrock College]]\n|'''28&ndash;16'''\n| [[Belvedere College]]\n|- style=\"background: #D0E6FF;\"\n| 1990\n| [[Blackrock College]]\n|'''14&ndash;6'''\n| [[Clongowes Wood College]]\n|-\n| 1991\n| [[Clongowes Wood College]]\n|'''7&ndash;3'''\n| [[St Michael's College, Dublin|St Michael's College]]\n|- style=\"background: #D0E6FF;\"\n| 1992\n| [[Terenure College]]\n|'''19&ndash;6'''\n| [[Belvedere College]]\n|-\n| 1993\n| [[Terenure College]]\n|'''8&ndash;3'''\n| [[Clongowes Wood College]]\n|- style=\"background: #D0E6FF;\"\n| 1994\n| [[St Mary's College, Dublin|St. Mary's College]]\n|'''14&ndash;14'''<br>'''7&ndash;3'''\n| [[Clongowes Wood College]]\n|-\n| 1995\n| [[Blackrock College]]\n|'''8&ndash;3'''\n| [[Clongowes Wood College]]\n|- style=\"background: #D0E6FF;\"\n| 1996\n| [[Blackrock College]]\n|'''37&ndash;3'''\n| [[Newbridge College]]\n|-\n| 1997\n| [[Terenure College]]\n|'''22&ndash;15'''\n| [[Clongowes Wood College]]\n|- style=\"background: #D0E6FF;\"\n| 1998\n| [[Clongowes Wood College]]\n|'''37&ndash;18'''\n| [[Terenure College]]\n|-\n| 1999\n| [[Blackrock  College]]\n|'''17&ndash;9'''\n| [[M.S.J. Roscrea|Cistercian, Roscrea]]\n|- style=\"background: #D0E6FF;\"\n| 2000\n| [[Clongowes Wood College]]\n|'''13&ndash;11'''\n| [[Terenure College]]\n|-\n| 2001\n| [[Terenure College]]\n|'''21&ndash;19'''\n| [[Blackrock College]]\n|- style=\"background: #D0E6FF;\"\n| 2002\n| [[St Mary's College, Dublin|St. Mary's College]]\n|'''10&ndash;6'''\n| [[Belvedere College]]\n|-\n| 2003\n| [[Terenure College]]\n|'''6&ndash;6'''<br>'''3&ndash;0'''\n| [[St Mary's College, Dublin|St. Mary's College]]\n|- style=\"background: #D0E6FF;\"\n| 2004\n| [[Blackrock College]]\n|'''24&ndash;9'''\n| [[Clongowes Wood College]]\n|-\n| 2005<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rte.ie/sport/rugby/2005/0317/190951-leinstersc/|title=Belvo take first senior cup win|accessdate=26 March 2015 |work=www.rte.ie |publisher= |date= 14 July 2007}}</ref>\n| [[Belvedere College]]\n|''